<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
{{> head pageTitle="Articles - Traditional Textile Stories"}}
<body>
{{> header}}

<main>
<style>
  /* Articles page specific styles using CSS variables */
  .articles-main {
    padding-top: var(--spacing-lg);
  }

  /* Hero section */
  .article-hero {
    text-align: center;
    padding: var(--spacing-3xl) var(--spacing-lg);
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary-color), #0e8aa940);
    color: white;
    border-radius: var(--border-radius-lg);
    margin: var(--spacing-lg) auto;
    max-width: 1200px;
    box-shadow: var(--box-shadow-lg);
  }

  .article-hero h1 {
    font-size: var(--font-size-3xl);
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-lg);
    color: white;
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .article-hero p {
    font-size: var(--font-size-lg);
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  /* Article layout */
  .article-container {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--spacing-2xl);
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: var(--spacing-2xl) auto;
    padding: 0 var(--spacing-lg);
  }

  .article-block {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: row;
    gap: var(--spacing-xl);
    align-items: flex-start;
    background: white;
    padding: var(--spacing-2xl);
    border-radius: var(--border-radius-lg);
    box-shadow: var(--box-shadow);
    transition: var(--transition);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
  }

  .article-block:hover {
    transform: translateY(-5px);
    box-shadow: var(--box-shadow-lg);
    border-color: var(--primary-color);
  }

  .article-block.reverse {
    flex-direction: row-reverse;
  }

  .image-container {
    position: relative;
    width: 350px;
    height: 280px;
    overflow: hidden;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    border-radius: var(--border-radius-lg);
    box-shadow: var(--box-shadow);
  }

  .image-container img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    display: block;
    border-radius: var(--border-radius-lg);
    transition: var(--transition);
  }

  .image-container:hover img {
    transform: scale(1.05);
  }

  .blur-overlay {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    border-radius: var(--border-radius-lg);
    background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
    opacity: 0;
    transition: var(--transition);
  }

  .card:hover .blur-overlay {
    opacity: 1;
  }

  .interaction-buttons {
    position: absolute;
    top: 50%;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
    opacity: 0;
    transition: var(--transition);
    z-index: 2;
  }

  .card:hover .interaction-buttons {
    opacity: 1;
  }

  .keyboard-button {
    padding: var(--spacing-md) var(--spacing-xl);
    border: none;
    border-radius: var(--border-radius);
    font-size: var(--font-size-base);
    font-weight: 600;
    cursor: pointer;
    background: var(--primary-color);
    color: white;
    transition: var(--transition);
  }

  .keyboard-button:hover {
    background: #1e4080;
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }

  .article-text {
    flex: 1;
  }

  .article-text h2 {
    font-size: var(--font-size-2xl);
    color: var(--text-dark);
    margin: 0 0 var(--spacing-lg) 0;
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .article-text p {
    font-size: var(--font-size-base);
    color: var(--text-light);
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin: var(--spacing-md) 0;
  }

  .article-title-link {
    color: var(--text-dark);
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: var(--transition);
  }

  .article-title-link:hover {
    color: var(--primary-color);
  }

  /* Responsive */
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .article-container {
      padding: 0 var(--spacing-md);
    }

    .article-block,
    .article-block.reverse {
      flex-direction: column;
      padding: var(--spacing-xl);
    }

    .image-container {
      width: 100%;
      height: 240px;
    }

    .article-hero {
      padding: var(--spacing-2xl) var(--spacing-md);
      margin: var(--spacing-md);
    }

    .article-hero h1 {
      font-size: var(--font-size-2xl);
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 576px) {
    .article-block {
      padding: var(--spacing-lg);
    }

    .image-container {
      height: 200px;
    }

    .article-hero h1 {
      font-size: var(--font-size-xl);
    }
  }
</style>

<section class="article-hero">
  <h1>Discover the Stories Behind Our Handmade Textiles</h1>
  <p>Every thread tells a story. Dive into the culture, history, and artistry of our traditional fabrics handcrafted by skilled artisans from Bhutan.</p>
</section>

<section class="article-container">
  <article class="article-block card">
    <div class="image-container">
      <img src="/productimage/A1.jpg" alt="Traditional Bhutanese Attire">
      <div class="blur-overlay"></div>
      <div class="interaction-buttons">
        <a href="/A1"><button class="keyboard-button">Explore</button></a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="article-text">
      <h2><a href="/A1" class="article-title-link">The Legacy of Bhutanese Weaving</a></h2>
      <p>Bhutanese textiles are globally renowned for their complexity, vibrant colors, and spiritual significance. Traditionally woven by women using backstrap looms, each piece represents regional patterns and clan identity.</p>
      <p>Our collection features patterns passed down for generations, woven in naturally dyed yarns and infused with personal symbolism. In rural communities, weaving is more than an art—it’s a form of storytelling.</p>
    </div>
  </article>

  <article class="article-block card reverse">
    <div class="image-container">
      <img src="/productimage/A2.jpeg" alt="Gho and Kira">
      <div class="blur-overlay"></div>
      <div class="interaction-buttons">
        <a href="/A2"><button class="keyboard-button">Explore</button></a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="article-text">
      <h2><a href="/A2" class="article-title-link">Origins of Traditional Dress</a></h2>
      <p>The history of Bhutanese textiles becomes more evident in the last century. As textile production moved beyond clothing to artistic expression of individuals and communities, royal patronage played a vital role.</p>
      <p>Lhuntse District, home to the most celebrated weavers, is also the ancestral place of the Wangchuck dynasty. The influence of royal women in preserving the weaving tradition is profound.</p>
    </div>
  </article>

  <article class="article-block card">
    <div class="image-container">
      <img src="/productimage/A3.jpg" alt="Trendy Textile">
      <div class="blur-overlay"></div>
      <div class="interaction-buttons">
        <a href="/A3"><button class="keyboard-button">Explore</button></a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="article-text">
      <h2><a href="/A3" class="article-title-link">Trendy Textile</a></h2>
      <p>Visitors to Bhutan often seek unique keepsakes beyond typical souvenirs. Our fashion-focused textiles offer modern aesthetics infused with tradition—perfect for those who want to stand out with style.</p>
    </div>
  </article>
</section>

{{> footer}}
</main>
</body>
</html>
